# Phase-2 Specification

## Problem Statement
Users need a simple web-based application to manage daily tasks effectively.

## User Story
As a user,
I want to create, view, update, complete, and delete tasks,
So that I can organize my daily work efficiently.

## Functional Requirements
- User can add a new task with a title
- User can view all tasks
- User can mark a task as completed or incomplete
- User can edit a task title
- User can delete a task

## Non-Functional Requirements
- Application must be responsive
- Backend APIs must return JSON
- UI updates should reflect backend state
- No authentication required in Phase-2

## Out of Scope
- User accounts
- Database persistence
- Advanced UI animations
